author: PlayStation
description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10014406

Embark on an unforgettable journey through Talos, a colossal fortress that has swallowed entire civilizations over the centuries. As Europa, a fierce warrior who has lost everything, you must battle through the corrupted depths of this labyrinthine stronghold, uncover its secrets, and bring life back to a world robbed of its colors.
With only your halberd and the aid of your spectral companion, Apino, you will confront tainted creatures, and harness elemental powers to overcome the looming curse.

Guided by the healing power of music, you will meet legendary composers who lend their talents to your quest.
9 Years of Shadows offers a rich and immersive experience, blending fast-paced combat, exploration, and a mesmerizing soundtrack featuring compositions by Michiru Yamane (Castlevania series) and Norihiko Hibino (Metal Gear Solid series).
Will you be the one to break the cycle of despair and restore the world’s lost harmony?

Key F
title: 9 Years of Shadows - Collector’s Edition | PS5 Games

author: PlayStation
description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/heroes-of-mount-dragon/

Unleash your inner dragon in Heroes of Mount Dragon! 🐉🔥

Soar into an action-packed, side-scrolling brawler where dragon-morphing powers, co-op chaos, and competitive mayhem collide. Choose from 5 unique dragon-bound heroes (with more coming soon), each with their own combat style and devastating dragon form.

Battle solo or team up with up to 3 friends in local or online co-op, smashing through hordes of enemies across vibrant, hand-crafted realms. Or turn your friends into rivals in wild competitive matches — complete with hilarious curses like inverted controls, shrink rays, and frog transformations!

⚡ Key Features
• Transform mid-battle into awe-inspiring dragons
• 4-player local & online multiplayer (co-op and versus)
• Distinct heroes with unique playstyles and combos
• Dynamic side-scrolling combat and fluid controls
• Striking 2.5D art that brings the world of Üna to life

#ps5 #ps5games
title: Heroes of Mount Dragon - Launch Trailer | PS5 Games

description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10015357

Set out to forge a new pirate utopia and bring justice to the traitors who wronged you in 'Republic of Pirates', a swashbuckling city builder with real-time naval combat, out now on PlayStation 5!

Develop a humble outpost into a sprawling settlement by investing in production buildings and amenities. Distribute valuable goods across a network of docks, depots, and warehouses, to address the needs of your citizens and increase their standing in pirate society. Recruit heroic captains and command a powerful fleet as you take to the waves in the name of conquest. Liberate islands, defeat rival factions, and navigate complex diplomatic relationships with the most influential national trading companies of the era.

#ps5 #ps5games #republicofpirates

Discover a bold, new story of a warrior in Japan who is on a mission of vengeance all her own.
